description:
=================================================================

This mod adds new spudguns. They look like famous guns from WW1 and WW2.
Some of them are animated so check them out if you like that kind of details!

Discord Server: https://discord.gg/QJRHhuUYsM

=================================================================

{value} - delay after shoot in ticks
[A] - gun is animated
<value> - amount of ammo in the magazine

====== NEW CONTENT ======

NEW EFFECTS:
- Muzzle Flash
- Case Ejecting
- Glowing Projectiles

NEW MOUNTABLE  WEAPON:
- Mac-31 [A] <150>

NEW HANDHELD WEAPON:
- Double Barrel Shotgun

=== LIGHT MACHINE GUNS ===

- [A] Lewis M1914  {4}
- [A] Maxim M1905  {4}
- Mac-31 [A] <150> {3}
- M1919 .30 {3}
- MG-34 {3}
- [A] MG-42 {2}, <50>
- DP-29 {4}
- DGx03 {4}

=== HEAVY MACHINE GUNS ===

- [A] Browning .50 {4}
- [A] Browning .50 Aircraft {4}
- DSzK 12.7mm {4}

====== 20mm CANNONS ======

- MG 151/20 {8}
- WZ.38 {10}
- Hispano {10}
- [A] Vulcan M61 {4}

======= EXPLOSIVES ========

- Bomb (proximity fuse)
- Bomb 50kg
- Bomb 100kg
- Bomb 250kg
- Anti-Tank Mine
- S-Mine

===== OTHER WEAPONS ======

- Bazooka {120}
- AK-47 {5}
- [A] Mosin-Nagant 1891 {100} <5>
- [A] PTRD-41 {120}
- [A] Cannon {160}

